printTabbedRdfContainer

public static java.lang.String printTabbedRdfContainer(int tabOffset,
                                                       java.lang.String tagName,
                                                       java.lang.String containerType,
                                                       RdfObject[] objects)
Static method for printing a tabbed rdf container (e.g. bag) in the following format: /t.../t /t.../t/t /t.../t/t/t // entry 1 in the container /t.../t/t/t/t[RdfObject - Can be simple or composite] /t.../t/t/t ... /t.../t/t/t // entry K in the container /t.../t/t/t/t[RdfObject - Can be simple or composite] /t.../t/t/t /t.../t/t /t.../t

Parameters:
tabOffset - - The base number of tags
tagName - - The wrapper tag name
containerType - - The type of the rdf-container (e.g. Bag)
objects - - The RdfObjects to be added in the container list
Returns:
- A string representation of the tabbed rdf container as defined above
